timing_extract...opagation_mode(25.10)  timing_extract...opagation_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_slew_propagation_mode

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_slew_propagation_mode

       {worst_slew | path_based_slew}

       Default: worst_slew

       Specifies  the type of slew propagation to use for generating extracted
       timing model (ETM).

       In worst slew propagation mode, the software propagates the worst  slew
       of all the incoming arcs at a converging point for extracting the arcs.

       In path based slew propagation mode, the software propagates the actual
       slew for the path elements for extracting the arcs.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

